        protected int parseColumns()
                    throws MZTabException

      • refine

        protected void refine()
               throws MZTabException
        Some validate operation need to be done after the whole MZTabColumnFactory created. Thus, user can add them, and called at the end of the MZTabHeaderLineParser.parse(int, String, MZTabErrorList) method. NOTICE: this method will be called at end of parse() function.
